    <title>阿里OSSFS工具实现OSS Bucket数据共享</title>
    <link href="http://qls-boy.github.io/2017/12/27/ossfs/"/>
    <id>http://qls-boy.github.io/2017/12/27/ossfs/</id>
    <published>2017-12-27T09:43:55.532Z</published>
    <updated>2017-12-27T09:43:55.528Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="简介"><a href="#简介" class="headerlink" title="简介"></a>简介</h2><p>OSSFS可以在Linux系统中将Aliyun OSS bucket挂载到本地文件系统中进行数据交互。根据官网信息目前只有Linux/CentOS/Ubuntu类操作系统的安装包。</p><h2 id="功能"><a href="#功能" class="headerlink" title="功能"></a>功能</h2><p>OSSFS 基于 s3fs 构建，具有 s3fs 的全部功能，主要功能包括：</p><ol><li>支持POSIX 文件系统的大部分功能，包括文件读写，目录，链接操作，权限，uid/gid，以及扩展属性（extended attributes）；</li><li>通过OSS 的multipart 功能上传大文件；</li><li>MD5 校验保证数据完整性。</li></ol><p>关于 s3fs 工具更多信息，可访问：<a href="http://s3fs.readthedocs.io/en/latest/index.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">URL</a></p><h2 id="局限性"><a href="#局限性" class="headerlink" title="局限性"></a>局限性</h2><p>OSSFS提供的功能和性能与本地文件系统相比，具有以下局限：</p><ol><li>随机或者追加写文件会导致整个文件的重写；</li><li>元数据操作，例如list directory，性能较差，因为需要远程访问OSS服务器；</li><li>文件/文件夹的rename操作不是原子的；</li><li>多个客户端挂载同一个OSS bucket时，依赖用户自行协调各个客户端的行为。例如避免多个客户端写同一个文件等等；</li><li>不支持hard link；</li><li>不适合用在高并发读/写的场景，这样会让系统的load升高。</li></ol><p>注：以上内容从阿里官网摘取而来。</p><h2 id="实施"><a href="#实施" class="headerlink" title="实施"></a>实施</h2><h3 id="1-下载并安装ossfs"><a href="#1-下载并安装ossfs" class="headerlink" title="1. 下载并安装ossfs"></a>1. 下载并安装ossfs</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ wget http://docs-aliyun.cn-hangzhou.oss.aliyun-inc.com/assets/attach/32196/cn_zh/1507811607579/ossfs_1.80.3_centos6.5_x86_64.rpm</span><br><span class="line">$ rpm -ivh ossfs_1.80.3_centos6.5_x86_64.rpm</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>若此处提示：<br>error: Failed dependencies:<br>        openssl-devel &gt;= 0.9 is needed by ossfs-1.80.3-1.x86_64<br>需要执行<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ yum install openssl-devel -y</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>安装完成后命令存放位置<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ ls -lh /usr/<span class="built_in">local</span>/bin/ossfs  </span><br><span class="line">-rwxr-xr-x 1 root root 4.0M Oct 12 16:35 /usr/<span class="built_in">local</span>/bin/ossfs</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>创建存储桶信息文件<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ <span class="built_in">echo</span> <span class="string">"my-bucket:my-access-key-id:my-access-key-secret"</span> &gt; /etc/passwd-ossfs</span><br><span class="line">$ chmod 640 /etc/passwd-ossfs <span class="comment">#阿里官网建议权限设置为640</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>挂载<br>格式：ossfs BUCKET:[PATH] MOUNTPOINT [OPTION]…<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ ossfs my-bucket my-mount-point(挂载点) -ourl=my-oss-endpoint(OSS域名)  <span class="comment">#挂载至桶所在根目录下</span></span><br><span class="line">$ ossfs my-bucket:/my-bucket-dir -ourl=my-oss-endpoint(OSS域名)  <span class="comment">#指定桶下具体存储位置</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>卸载<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ fusermount -u my-mount-point</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>设置开机自挂载<br>方式1：修改 fstab<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ vim /etc/fstab</span><br><span class="line">ossfs<span class="comment">#your_bucket_name your_mount_point fuse _netdev,url=your_url,allow_other 0 0 </span></span><br><span class="line">$ mount -a <span class="comment">#确保fstab配置正常</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>若开机重启后发现无法自动挂载，需要将netfs服务设置开机自启动<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ chkconfig netfs on</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>方式2：命令自启<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ <span class="built_in">echo</span> <span class="string">"/usr/local/bin/ossfs my-bucket my-mount-point -ourl=my-oss-endpoint"</span> &gt;&gt; /etc/rc.local</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>参考链接<br>阿里官网OSSFS工具：<br><a href="https://help.aliyun.com/document_detail/32196.html?spm=5176.doc50452.6.1052.r0tzpq" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://help.aliyun.com/document_detail/32196.html?spm=5176.doc50452.6.1052.r0tzpq</a><br>阿里官网OSSFS工具FAQ：<br><a href="https://help.aliyun.com/document_detail/32197.html?spm=5176.11065259.1996646101.searchclickresult.6ed76232bnkxN2" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://help.aliyun.com/document_detail/32197.html?spm=5176.11065259.1996646101.searchclickresult.6ed76232bnkxN2</a></p>]]></content>
    
